[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "COUNT CAGLIOSTRO, ALIAS JOSEPH BALSAMO, KNOWN ALSO AS \"CURSED JOE.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "He was born at Palermo, in seventeen forty three, and very early began to manifest his brilliant talents for roguery.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "He ran away from his first boarding school, at the age of eleven or twelve, getting up a masquerade of goblins, by the aid of some scampish schoolfellows, which frightened the monkish watchmen of the gates away from their posts, nearly dead with terror.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "His final offence was a ridiculous and characteristic one.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "After this, Master Joe proceeded to distinguish himself by forging opera tickets, and even documents of various kinds, indiscriminate pilfering and swindling, interpreting visions, conjuring, and finally, it is declared, a touch of genuine assassination.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "Pretty soon he made a foolish, greedy goldsmith, one Marano, believe that there was a treasure hidden in the sand on the sea shore near Palermo, and induced the silly man to go one night to dig it up.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "Almost instantly, six devils, horned, hoofed, tailed, and clawed, breathing fire and smoke, leaped from among the rocks and beat the wretched goldsmith senseless, and almost to death.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "They were of course Cursed Joe and some confederates; and taking Marano's money and valuables, they left him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "He got home in wretched plight, but had sense enough left to suspect Master Joe, whom he shortly promised, after the Sicilian manner, to assassinate.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000006_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000006_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "So Joe ran away from Palermo, and went to Messina.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000006_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000006_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "This feat made not only a sensation but plenty of money; and the two swindlers now traversed Greece, Turkey, and Arabia, in various directions, stirring up the Oriental \"old fogies\" in amazing style.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000006_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000006_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "Pinto was an alchymist, and had been fooled to the top of his bent by the cunning Joseph.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "These letters introduced our humbug into the first families of Rome; who, like some other first families, were first also as fools.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "He also married a very beautiful, very shrewd, and very wicked Roman donzella, Lorenza Feliciani by name; and the worthy couple, combining their various talents, and regarding the world as their oyster, at once proceeded to open it in the most scientific style.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "This degree was to give perfection to human beings, by means of moral and physical regeneration.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000008_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000008_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "Of these two the former was to be secured by means of a Pentagon, which removes original sin and renews pristine innocence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000008_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000008_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "The physical kind of regeneration was to be brought about by using the \"prime matter\" or philosopher's stone, and the \"Acacia,\" which two ingredients will give immortal youth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000008_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000008_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "In fact, this pretension, which influenced thousands upon thousands of believers, was one of the most daring impostures that ever saw the light; and it is astounding to think that, so late as seventeen eighty, it should, for a long time, have been entirely successful.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000008_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000008_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "and ending in \"physical regeneration\" and an immortality on earth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "In seventeen seventy six, the Count and Countess came to London.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "Here, funnily enough, they fell into the hands of a gambler, a shyster, and a female scamp, who together tormented them almost to death, because the Count would not pick them out lucky numbers to gamble by.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "One incident of Cagliostro's English experience was the affair of the \"Arsenical Pigs\"--a notice of which may be found in the \"Public Advertiser,\" of London of september third seventeen eighty six.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "Among other new dodges, he now assumed so supernatural a piety that (he said) he could distinguish an unbeliever by the smell! which, of course, was just the opposite of the \"odor of sanctity.\" The Count's claim to have lived for hundreds of years was, by some, thoroughly believed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "He ascribed his immortality to his own Elixir, and his comparatively youthful appearance to his \"Water of Beauty,\" his Countess readily assisting him by speaking of her son, a Colonel in the Dutch service, fifty years old, while she appeared scarcely more than twenty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185517_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185517/4277_185517_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "The celebrated story of \"The Diamond Necklace,\" in which Cagliostro, Marie Antoinette, the Cardinal de Rohan, and others were mixed in such a hodge podge of rascality and folly, must form a narrative by itself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185519_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185519/4277_185519_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "GERMAIN, SAGE, PROPHET, AND MAGICIAN.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185519_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185519/4277_185519_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "The most plausible theory, however, makes him the natural son of an Italian princess, and fixes his birth at San Germano, in Savoy, about the year seventeen ten; his ostensible father being one Rotondo, a tax collector of that district.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185519_000004_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185519/4277_185519_000004_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "But it was in alectromancy, or divination by signs and circles; hydromancy, or divination by water; cleidomancy, or divination by the key, and dactylomancy, or divination by the fingers, that the count chiefly excelled, although he, at the same time, professed alchemy, astrology, and prophecy in the higher branches.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185519_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185519/4277_185519_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "In England, he was the inseparable friend of Prince Lobkowitz-a circumstance that gave some color to his alleged connection with the Russians.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185519_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185519/4277_185519_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "His birth, he said, had been in Chaldea, in the dawn of time; and that he was the sole inheritor of the lost sciences and mysteries of his own and the Egyptian race.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185519_000005_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185519/4277_185519_000005_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "His predictions were, indeed, most startling; and the cotemporaneous evidence is very strong and explicit, that he did foretell the time, place, and manner of the death of Louis the fifteenth, several years before it occurred.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185519_000005_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185519/4277_185519_000005_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "His gift of memory was perfectly amazing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185519_000005_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185519/4277_185519_000005_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "He would, however, have been ineligible for any faithful Post Office, since he read the contents of sealed letters at a glance; and, by his clairvoyant powers, detected crime, or, in fact, the movements of men and the phenomena of nature, at any distance.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185519_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185519/4277_185519_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "Still another peculiarity of the Count would be highly advantageous to any of us, particularly at this period of high prices and culinary scarcity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4277_185519_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4277/185519/4277_185519_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4277",
        "content": "He never ate nor drank; or, at least, he was never seen to do so!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
